  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Audit Framework Agreement 2015-2019</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">Upphandling revisionsramavtal Kigali 2015-2019    Dec nr KIG P 38-14</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">PLEASE REVIEW YOUR ANSWER AS THE QUESTION HAS BEEN CHANGED

Svenska ambassaden i Kigali avser att upphandla ett ramavtal f&#xF6;r revisionstj&#xE4;nster med syfet att
1) ge ambassaden m&#xF6;jlighet att upphandla olika typer av revisionstj&#xE4;nster
2) assistera ambassaden och samarbetspartners att bygga intern kapacitet vad g&#xE4;ller revision
3) att p&#xE5; en ad hoc bas assistera med fr&#xE5;gor som uppkommer med kort varsel och som kan besvaras samma dag via mail eller telefon, d.v.s. en sorts lokal &quot;help desk&quot; vad g&#xE4;ller revisionsfr&#xE5;gor

Ramavtal &#xE4;mnas tecknas med h&#xF6;gst 3 parter - under 120 timmar rankat och &#xF6;ver 120 timmer f&#xF6;rnyad konkurrensuts&#xE4;ttning. Denna insats inneh&#xE5;ller dels sj&#xE4;lva ramavtalet och dels utnyttjandet a v ramavtalet, d.v.s. varje call off blir en utbetalning under denna insats. Detta f&#xF6;r att h&#xE5;lla ihop revisionstj&#xE4;nsterna och ha kontroll &#xF6;ver hur mycket som avropas och till vad mm.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This contribution puts in place a framework for audit services through an open tender procurement process. The aim is:
(1)	to give the Embassy of Sweden in Rwanda the possibility to undertake different types of auditing and related services including financial assurance and non-assurance audits and other audit related services 

(2)	to assist the Embassy and counterpart institutions, authorities and organizations in building internal capacity relating to audit activities.

(3)	to assist on and ad-hoc basis in less complicated audit advice that can be given by telephone or e-mail within a day

The agreement will be ranked for assignment up to 120 hours and renewed competition will be undertaken for all assignments above 120 hours. The ambition is to sign agreement with max 3 firms</narrative>
  </description>
